sign~
Welcome to the world-renowed Kir Drax'in Zoo!
Our Attractions:
    o  The Aviary (in the north wing) For Levels 1-2
    o  Our "Wild Animals in Captivity" (in the west wing)
       For Levels 3 and up, with each room getting wilder!
    o  Our "Rare and Exotic" Collection. (in the east wing)
       For Levels 4-6

Please mind our zookeepers, who are there for your protection,
as well as the protection of the animals.
Thank you.
