#14502
Westwing Exhibits~
   You are standing at the start of the west wing.  Loud shrieks and screams
emanate from the room north of here, while the south is strangely quiet.  
Just outside the atrium marks the start of a paved walkway for the west wing
exhibits.  A cacophany of wild animal sounds emanates from all directions.  
Flanking the south and north walls are two exhibits.  Sounds of shrieks are
loudest here and seem to be coming from the north.  The walkway continues
westward towards more exhibits.  
