End of the Westwing Exhibits~
   The paved walkway ends here with the final exhibits to your north and
south.  To the west a small seating area has been arranged with three benches
forming a half circle.  Lush green plants in clay pots sit at the end of each
bench.  To the the north lies an exhibit blocked off by chains for
